  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/156235556/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u156235556-4.jpg" class="pil" alt="甜不厌食" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/156235556/">甜不厌食</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          2月11日          在读      </div>

        <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
      <br/>

      <span class="pl">tags:澳门 近代中国 全球史观</span><br />

    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/92019270/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u92019270-6.jpg" class="pil" alt="一尺木" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/92019270/">一尺木</a><br/>
      <div class="pl ll">          1月18日          想读      </div>

      <br/>


    </div>
    <div class="clear"></div><br/>
    <div class="ul" style="margin-bottom:12px;"></div>
</div>
<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/InTheAmericas/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u43352004-4.jpg" class="pil" alt="南北美洲之间" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/InTheAmericas/">南北美洲之间</a><br/>
